                58

                59

                60

                61

  pub fn fill<I: IntoIterator<Item = A::Item>>(

            

        

            

                459
            

            

                
            

            

                
    &mut self, iter: I,

            

        

            

                460
            

            

                
            

            

                
  ) -> I::IntoIter {

            

        

            

                461

                462
            

            

                
            

            

                
    // compiler emits code that updates the length for every element. The

            

        

            

                463
            

            

                
            

            

                
    // additional complexity from that length update is worth nearly 2x in

            

        

            

                464

                470

                471

                472
            

            

                
            

            

                
    }

            

        

            

                473
            

            

                
            

            

                
    self.len += pushed as u16;

            

        

            

                474
            

            

                
            

            

                
    iter

            

        

            

                475
            

            

                
            

            

                
  }
